urls.title: How do I add seats to my reservation? · Spirit Airlines Support
urls.description: Simply go to the My Trips tab and follow the instructions to access your reservation. If you are accessing your reservation more than 24 hours prior to departure you can click the Add or Modify Seats link and complete the form. If you are accessing your reservation within 24 hours prior to departure (up to 1.5 hours prior to departure) you must purchase seats through online check-in process. Keywords: clm:topic:optcha,clm:topic:seacha,seats,seat selection,sit together Copyright © 2022 Spirit Airlines,

urls.title: Does Spirit offer U.S. Military discounts? · Spirit Airlines Support
urls.description: The best thing we can do for members of the U.S. military, is to keep their fares as low as possible. Understanding the special thanks the U.S. military members deserve, Spirit is proud to provide the following services: Free Bags For Active Duty U.S. Military For active duty military traveling on Spirit, we will provide two free checked bags and a free carry-on, in addition to the already free personal item. The U.S. military member should arrive early enough to have their bags checked at the counter,

data.text: As a thanks for their service, all active duty U.S. military 🇺🇸 of United States can have their luggage fly free. Learn more here 👉 https://t.co/2h5jKiUSgD https://t.co/cx9udFsHWg
